---
import Layout from '../layouts/StaticPageLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Write for Us - InvisibleText.me";
const pageDescription = "Contribute original content to InvisibleText.me. Learn how to submit guest posts, our writing guidelines, and the benefits of guest blogging.";
---
<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <section class="prose mx-auto px-4 py-10 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center p-2">Write for InvisibleText.me</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 py-4">
        Thank you for your interest in contributing to <strong>InvisibleText.me</strong>! We're looking for passionate writers who can bring unique and engaging content to our readers. Whether you're a tech enthusiast, Unicode expert, or creative educator, we'd love to hear from you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold py-4">Why Write for Us?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 ">
        <li>Share your expertise with a growing audience interested in invisible and blank characters</li>
        <li>Gain exposure on a well-established niche site</li>
        <li>Connect with like-minded individuals and communities</li>
        <li>Enhance your personal brand and online presence</li>
        <li>Receive recognition as a guest author on our platform</li>
        <li>Improve your writing skills and learn from feedback</li>
        <li>Contribute to a unique topic that’s not widely covered</li>
        <li>Help others discover the fascinating world of invisible text and characters</li>
        <li>Boost your SEO with high-quality backlinks</li>
        <li>Expand your network within the tech and writing communities</li>
        <li>Participate in a collaborative and supportive environment</li>
        <li>Contribute to a resource that educates and informs</li>
        <li>Get featured on a site that values quality content</li>
        <li>Receive constructive feedback to improve your writing</li>
        <li>Engage with a community that appreciates unique content</li>
        <li>Have your work shared on our social media channels</li>
        <li>Contribute to a site that values creativity and innovation</li>
        <li>Help us grow our content library with fresh perspectives</li>
        <li>Participate in a platform that encourages diverse voices</li>
        <li>Gain insights into the world of Unicode and text manipulation</li>
        <li>Learn about the latest trends in online content creation</li>
        <li>Contribute to discussions around online productivity and creativity</li>
        <li>Help us explore the creative uses of invisible and special characters</li>
        <li>Be part of a project that aims to educate and inspire</li>
        <li>Share your passion for language, symbols, and digital communication</li>
        <li>Contribute to a site that values originality and authenticity</li>
        <li>Help us build a comprehensive resource for invisible text enthusiasts</li>    
        <li>Earn high-quality backlinks to support your SEO strategy</li>
        <li>Increase referral traffic to your website</li>
        <li>Build your online authority and brand</li>
        <li>Share your knowledge with a niche audience</li>
        <li>Grow your writing portfolio</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold py-4">Topics We Welcome</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 ">We’re open to a variety of topics related to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 ">
        <li>Invisible and blank characters</li>
        <li>Unicode tips and tricks</li>
        <li>Special characters in gaming or online usernames</li>
        <li>Creative uses of symbols in text and design</li>
        <li>Online productivity tools and text manipulation</li>
        <li>Educational uses of invisible text and characters</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold py-4">Submission Guidelines</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 ">
        <li><strong>Originality:</strong> Content must be 100% original and written by a human—no AI-generated articles.</li>
        <li><strong>Relevance:</strong> Posts should align with our niche and add real value to our audience.</li>
        <li><strong>Length:</strong> Articles should be between <strong>1000–1500 words</strong>.</li>
        <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Clear, engaging writing with correct grammar and formatting is a must.</li>
        <li><strong>Formatting:</strong> Use headings, short paragraphs, bullet points, and visuals where appropriate.</li>
        <li><strong>No spam:</strong> Avoid keyword stuffing, rewritten content, or irrelevant promotional links.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold py-4">How to Submit</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 ">
        Ready to contribute? Reach out to us via email with your topic idea or draft. You can also find us using these search operators:
      </p>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-md my-4">
      <pre class="bg-gray-100 border p-4 rounded-md text-sm text-gray-800">
  "invisible character" + "write for us"
  "blank space" + "guest post"
  "unicode symbol" + "submit article"
  "invisible text" + "become a contributor"
  "special character" + "submit guest post"
  "hidden character" + "write for us"
  "ghost character" + "guest post"
  "hidden text" + "submit article"
  "blank symbol" + "become a contributor"
  "hidden text" + "submit guest post"
  "ghost text" + "write for us"
  "hidden unicode" + "guest post"
  "blank unicode" + "submit article"      
  "invisible symbol" + "write for us"
  "blank character" + "guest post"
  "unicode character" + "submit article"
  "invisible text" + "become a contributor"
  "special characters in text" + "submit guest post"
      </pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-center font-semibold py-4 ">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg my-4"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">What is guest posting?</h3><p class="text-gray-600 ">It’s the practice of writing content for another website as a guest author to share your expertise and gain exposure.</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg my-4"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Do you offer do-follow backlinks?</h3><p class="text-gray-600 ">Yes, we provide do-follow links in approved guest posts.</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg my-4"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">How do I submit a post?</h3><p class="text-gray-600 ">Email us your draft or topic proposal. We’ll review it and get back to you promptly.</p></div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 shadow-sm rounded-lg my-4"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">What are the benefits?</h3><p class="text-gray-600 ">Aside from backlinks, you’ll build authority, expand your audience, and be featured on a well-trafficked niche site.</p></div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-gray-600">
        <strong>Join our community of writers and help us explore the fascinating world of invisible text!</strong> Ready to write? Email us at:<a href="mailto:contact@InvisibleText.me" class="relative inline-block after:absolute after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:h-[1px] after:bg-current hover:after:animate-grow-line hover:text-black">contact@InvisibleText.me</a><strong> We look forward to your submission!</strong> For questions or article pitches visit our contact page.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
